title: What lies do K-pop idols often tell their companies? - Quora

response.answer_text: I only heard that when K-pop idols diet, they lie to their managers by eating secretly. wise words said by them : Seulgi (Red Velvet) "We made it hard on our managers because we kept eating chicken behind their backs. I like oily foods so we ordered chicken in secret."  Chanmi (AOA) “I couldn't pass the monthly weight because I ate tteokbokki”  Seolhyun (AOA) “I had to write the list of foods that I consumed when I was going through my weight assessment. I said I wrote just pumpkin and cabbage instead of pastries and snacks that I had actually eaten. Therefore, I got in trouble.”  RM And V (BTS) “I had walked into a Big Hit employee when I was eating ice cream with V. Because this sweet dessert causes weight gain and is forbidden to idol trainees, me and V had to put the ice cream in our pockets and take it out again to eat it once the employee was out of sight.”   RM again (BTS) “I craved jjajangmyeon so much that I lied and went to the bathroom to eat it. I also finished it in two bites because I wanted to rush back”  Jokbal ; all members (TWICE) “We ordered this dish but used shoelace ties to have it delivered through our window. We ordered the dish but did not want to be caught by our managers or be caught on surveillance cameras so we decided to secretly get it through our window.” -Tzuyu   YooA (Oh My Girl) “I had gone to a hamburger store and was eating a hamburger when I saw an employee from my company. So I ran into the bathroom to finish my burger.  -choiseunghyun Seven dishes that idols were forbidden to eat as trainees
